"settingsWalkThroughPathColorText" = "Clew shows the route path by displaying a virtual line that intersects with the waypoints or crumbs. Please select a color for your path line from the list. Tip: You can make the path line a different color from the crumb in order to improve contrast between them.";
"settingsWalkThroughFeedbackOptionsTitle" = "Feedback";
"settingsWalkThroughFeedbackOptionsText" = "Clew provides sounds, haptic (vibration) feedback and voice cues to help you navigate a route. You can turn these ON/OFF at any time in the Settings. But, we recommend that you at least keep one mode of feedback active in order to have the best experience with Clew. Tip: new users are encouraged to keep all feedback modes on.";
