"settingsWalkThroughPhoneBodyOffsetTextParagraph2" = "Clew's Automatic Phone Pose & Alignment Correction feature helps correct for any offset or changes to the pose of your phone. It's especially useful for users who have difficulty perceiving their phone's spatial orientation or direction during travel and will make the navigation with Clew more accurate.";
